# Leacme.Theremy

**Leacme Theremy** is a cross-platform application that is currently targeted for mobile devices. It is build using the [Godot Engine](https://github.com/godotengine/godot).

This application features the ability to simulate the musical instrument Theremin.

![][image_screenshot]
![index](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6654513/71704240-61f4d100-2d96-11ea-8731-9fa59b28dfcc.png)

## Application Compiling

The application can be compiled into the platform-specific executable with the Godot Engine via the following [instructions](https://docs.godotengine.org/en/latest/getting_started/workflow/export/index.html). Make sure to run `nuget restore` to fetch dependencies specified in the .csproj file prior to building with Godot.

## Application Usage

Drag your finger on the screen vertically to change the volume and horizontally to change the pitch.
